               topics include: Mobert Bonhomme; Nagano Eiji (Japanese
               General); Chaplain W. F. McClain; Mrs. Lemuel C.
               Shepherd; Guam Liberation Day; a form letter for the
               sympathy message sent to parents of soldiers killed in
               action.</p>
